site_name: New Tuke School; Saul, Sharpness & Painswick Courts
description: Change of use and redevelopment land at Saul, Sharpness and Painswich Court to provide new single storey secondary school for students with profound learning difficulties, with access, parking, amenity space and closure of a section of Longhope Close (running north/south parallel to Gloucester Primary School) and an approximate 30m length of Daniel Gardens (at its western most end adjoining Longhope Close)
